s.com.cn|access-date=6 February 2020 |language=Chinese}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-113\">{{cite web|url=http://www.nbd.com.cn/articles/2020-02-06/1405947.html |script-title=zh:\u7d2f\u8ba1\u786e\u8bca\u65b0\u51a0\u80ba\u708e600\u4f8b \u6c5f\u897f\u5168\u7701\u6240\u6709\u6751\u7ec4\u5c0f\u533a\u4e00\u5f8b\u5c01\u95ed\u7ba1\u7406|website=nbd.com.cn|access-date=6 February 2020 |language=Chinese}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-114\">{{cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/sh/2020/02-06/9081041.shtml|script-title=zh:\u54b8\u9633\u51fa\u53f0\u75ab\u60c5\u9632\u63a7\u5341\u6761\u63aa\u65bd \u6bcf\u6237\u6bcf\u5468\u53ef\u4e24\u6b21\u6307\u6d3e1\u4eba\u5916\u91c7-\u4e2d\u65b0\u7f51|website=chinanews.com|language=zh-cn|access-date=6 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-115\">{{cite web|url=http://www.1m3d.com/thread-591947-1-1.html|script-title=zh:\u9526\u5dde\u5e02\u65b0\u578b\u51a0\u72b6\u75c5\u6bd2\u611f\u67d3\u7684\u80ba\u708e \u75ab\u60c5\u9632\u63a7\u6307\u6325\u90e8\u4ee4 \u7b2c4\u53f7 |trans-title=Order for Prevention and Control of Pneumonia of New Coronavirus Infection in Jinzhou City No. 4 |date=6 February 2020|url-status=live|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206172140/http://www.1m3d.com/thread-591947-1-1.html |archive-date=7 February 2020|access-date=6 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-116\">{{cite web|url=http://jl.sina.com.cn/news/b/2020-02-06/detail-iimxxste9261682.shtml |script-title=zh:\u957f\u6625\u5e02\u5bbd\u57ce\u533a\uff1a\u6bcf\u6237\u5bb6\u5ead\u6bcf\u4e24\u5929\u53ef\u6d3e\u4e00\u4eba\u51fa\u95e8\u91c7\u8d2d\u751f\u6d3b\u7269\u8d44|publisher=Sina Corp|access-date=6 February 2020 |language=Chinese}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-117\">{{cite web|url=http://www.chinanews.com/sh/2020/02-06/9081537.shtml|script-title=zh:\u6cb3\u5317\u5510\u5c71\u5bf9\u6240\u6709\u6751\u5e84\u3001\u5c0f\u533a\u3001\u5355\u4f4d\u5b9e\u884c\u5c01\u95ed\u5f0f\u7ba1\u7406|website=chinanews.com|access-date=7 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"AutoDW-118\">{{cite web |url=http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2020-02/16/content_5479534.htm |script-title=zh:\u5404\u5730\u903e2.5\u4e07\u540d\u533b\u7597\u961f\u5458\u652f\u63f4\u6e56\u5317|date=16 February 2020|work=People's Daily|language=Chinese}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Outbreak\">{{cite news |url=https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202001230201.aspx |date=23 January 2020 |language=zh |script-title=zh:\u6bd4\u7167SARS\u96c6\u4e2d\u91ab\u6cbb \u6b66\u6f22\u64ec6\u5929\u5efa\u5343\u5e8a\u91ab\u7642\u7ad9 \u2013 \u5169\u5cb8 \u2013 \u91cd\u9ede\u65b0\u805e |access-date=23 January 2020 |agency=[[Central News Agency (Taiwan)|Central News Agency]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"20200128www\">{{cite web |url=http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2020-01/28/content_5472565.htm |script-title=zh:\u674e\u514b\u5f3a\u7763\u6218\u6b66\u6c49\"\u5c0f\u6c64\u5c71\"\u533b\u9662\u5efa\u8bbe\uff1a\u628a\u8fd9\u91cc\u5efa\u6210\u904f\u5236\u75ab\u60c5\u8513\u5ef6\u7684\"\u5b89\u5168\u5c9b\" |date=28 January 2020 |website=gov.cn|language=Chinese}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Xinhua Huoshenshan\">{{Cite news |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/english/2020-01/24/c_138731107.htm |title=Wuhan to follow Beijing's SARS treatment model in new coronavirus control |date=24 January 2020 |access-date=24 January 2020 |agency=Xinhua News Agency}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"20200124theguardian-plans\">{{cite news | last=Siddique | first=Haroon | title=Chinese city plans to build coronavirus hospital in days | website=[[The Guardian]] | date=24 January 2020 | url=http://www.theguardian.com/science/2020/jan/24/chinese-city-wuhan-plans-to-build-coronavirus-hospital-in-six-days | access-date=13 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"chinanews9069083\">{{Cite news |last=Xu |first=Jinbo |url=http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2020/01-25/9069083.shtml |date=25 January 2020 |access-date=25 January 2020 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125151457/http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2020/01-25/9069083.shtml |archive-date=25 January 2020 |agen