imler.com/dccom/0-5-7171-1-1359454-1-0-0-0-0-0-12037-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0.html |title=Successful Year for Mercedes-Benz: Sales Up 15 Percent Worldwide in 2010 &#124; Daimler > Investor Relations > Capital Market Releases |publisher=Daimler |accessdate=2011-12-03 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111002044940/http://www.daimler.com/dccom/0-5-7171-1-1359454-1-0-0-0-0-0-12037-0-0-0-0-0-0-0-0.html |archivedate=2011-10-02 }}</ref>||60,922|| 139,192|| 40,760<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mercedes-benz.com.cn/content/china/mpc/mpc_china_website/enng/home_mpc/passengercars/home/passengercars_world/news/2011_News/115_Growth_Mercedes-Benz_Remains_China_s_Fastest_Growing_Premium_brand_in_2010.html |title=Mercedes-Benz China Homepage \u2013 2011 News \u2013 115% Growth \u2013 Mercedes-Benz Remains China's Fastest Growing Premium brand in 2010 |publisher=Mercedes-benz.com.cn |date= |accessdate=2011-12-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Hg6faXQW?url=http://www.mercedes-benz.com.cn/content/china/mpc/mpc_china_website/enng/home_mpc/passengercars/home/passengercars_world/news/2011_News/115_Growth_Mercedes-Benz_Remains_China_s_Fastest_Growing_Premium_brand_in_2010.html |archive-date=2013-06-27 |url-status=dead }}</ref>\n|-\n| 2011\n| 338,386 || 62,736<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/mercedes-benz-usa-hits-its-highest-ever-us-volume-with-sales-of-305072-185567602.html |title=Mercedes-Benz USA Hits Its Highest-Ever U.S. Volume With Sales of 305,072 |author=Mercedes-Benz USA |date=3 January 2013 |work=prnewswire.com}}</ref> || 129,963|| 44,738\n|-\n| 2012\n| 310,408 || 65,171 || 98,142|| 36,385\n\n|-\n| 2013\n| || 69,803 || 106,559|| 36,836\n|-\n| 2014\n| - (257,571 / - / - )|| 66,400<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/mercedes-benz-delivers-record-breaking-2014-sales-volume-of-330391-up-57-300015788.html |title=Mercedes-Benz Delivers Record-Breaking 2014 Sales Volume of 330,391, Up 5.7% |publi